  "body": "In a cloud provider environment it's possible to use up the API quota grinding the cluster to a halt: \n\nhttps://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/31858\n\nIn a multi tenant environment, one user could consume the quota for an entire cluster.  Some cloud providers allow throttling of API calls by type but Kube does not differentiate on the call types, so DOS still possible.\n",
